# Product context

Tracebud MVP is EUDR-only and multi-tenant.

## Mandatory read-order before major changes

1. `TRACEBUD_V1_2_EUDR_SPEC.md`
2. `REQUIREMENTS.md`
3. `MVP_PRD.md`
4. `PRODUCT_PRD.md`
5. `JTBD_PRD.md`
6. `BUILD_READINESS_ARTIFACTS.md`
7. Relevant `product-os/*` files (feature/workflow/quality/status)

If conflicts exist, earlier items in this order win.

## Alias mapping

- `requirement.md` means `REQUIREMENTS.md`
- `PRODUCT_PDR.md` means `PRODUCT_PRD.md`
- `tracebud v1.6 spec` means `TRACEBUD_V1_2_EUDR_SPEC.md` (canonical file currently contains v1.6 content)
